{"tid":197293,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一個絲打獨(毒)遊歐洲，遊記之你問我答","createTime":"2017-04-11T19:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T13:31:37.000Z","uid":77001,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04c2a6f8b4651c84b3e5cf6cdc12b5d75032e01d","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T19:59:33.000Z","msg":"我係三月嘅時候好急咁決定左4月3號去旅行<br />\n當時買左$4000 維也納來回機票，因為有識人住係嗰度，所以會係維也納hea耐少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係德國悶得濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家由4月3號開始打起<br />\n我4月3號飛台灣，會停係台灣13個鐘，所以係台灣玩左陣先返機場<br />\n以下係我今次嘅行程<br />\n4.3       HK✈️Taipei✈️Vienna <br />\n4.4-4.6       Vienna<br />\n4.7       Vienna🚊Salzburg <br />\n4.8       Salzburg <br />\n4.9       Salzburg 🚍Hallstatt<br />\n4.10      Hallstatt🚍salzburg🚍Munich<br />\n4.11      Munich <br />\n4.12      Munich 🚍Berchtesgaden<br />\n4.13      Berch 🚍Munich<br />\n4.14      Munich🚊天鵝堡<br />\n4.15      Munich🚍Prague <br />\n4.16      Prague  🚍Kutna Hora🚍Prague<br />\n4.17      Prague 🚍ck🚍Prague <br />\n4.18      Prague🚊wroclaw <br />\n4.19      wroclaw <br />\n4.20      wroclaw🚍krakow<br />\n4.21      krakow <br />\n4.22      krakow<br />\n4.23-27 Vienna"},{"pid":"f62490917087930b9b1cfbc6482f2c25a6174aca","tid":197293,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a60c2b6384945ccf8a506108e4c8e0b3ef29f48","tid":197293,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:03:14.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e940cb90b96752b0b1c7061315f3a757e3c321","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:03:33.000Z","msg":"4月3號<br />\n我都唔知我係台灣做左乜野，好似淨係食食食<br />\n⼃<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/040325_e89568bf33410ba0fcfa12c6d95d7bb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F040325_e89568bf33410ba0fcfa12c6d95d7bb0.jpg&h=7cbd54f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43200beedad704ad3092974fafa6d4ca5e4ac69a","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:09:41.000Z","msg":"不過我有樣野好好奇，點解d台灣咁搞笑整呢d岀黎，我見到得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又真係幾大，圖2五顏六色好似唔食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗係蠟燭。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/040722_4e76f77996b39f00c4cb4ae3ec147cd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F040722_4e76f77996b39f00c4cb4ae3ec147cd6.jpg&h=2ed9730d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/040800_ab5386be3a5ca40064bee2a0b4943c37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F040800_ab5386be3a5ca40064bee2a0b4943c37.jpg&h=612de653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我只係路過台灣，所以都冇點去搵其他野食，求其做下女人應做嘅野---shopping <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後去左士林夜市食少少野就返機場，沖個涼就上機"},{"pid":"4b1b99d1c37f9a2b6154b5fbe4b23a254b81c0e7","tid":197293,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:10:31.000Z","msg":"bam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4760b7ec6b0f2a6be3bc85b290210e0fef67bb","tid":197293,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:11:55.000Z","msg":"蠟燭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b210aa601ff6b2788ede7ee5f4d821b886adb12e","tid":197293,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:19:39.000Z","msg":"15號由CK落munich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d964b9576e007fc888ba1fd6b1213bb38ec3d4d","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:24:23.000Z","msg":"我係台北桃園機場飛夜晚23:30，去到Vienna 係朝早6:00，好彩有人接我機，而我就可以唔洗用腦就去到佢住嘅地方，因為佢係呢邊讀書嘅關係，住嗰d student apartment 都幾大下，問過大約$3500 1個月，返到佢屋企我訓左陣，下午2點岀左門口<br />\n首先梗係填飽個肚先，去左間類似快餐店但就即場order即場煮俾你嘅連鎖店，我叫左個risotto，食完飽到上心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多本地人都食呢間，價錢大約$90港幣，歐洲黎講都正常掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TaVFx49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTaVFx49.jpg&h=5906c321&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/042214_b4532cf91ea073e37dc872aa7d84d122.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F042214_b4532cf91ea073e37dc872aa7d84d122.jpg&h=4bc1c3aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c71565d41a93762634c6f3898404fe68dbdf87c4","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>15號由CK落munich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我而家係munich，聽朝7:30巴士去Berchtesgaden<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baa8d2479157a4328094628a918c19c0d49f994","tid":197293,"uid":33897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:36:57.000Z","msg":"salzburg除左去國王湖仲有咩玩"},{"pid":"96a79b6a5b3f8b2d3402029376fc3351eec25545","tid":197293,"uid":1666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T20:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文盲的me"},{"pid":"f691bfee0894ddd9a203bffb3d629e1ac28626cf","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:00:43.000Z","msg":"4月4號<br />\n食完個lunch就直接去左stephansdom 斯蒂芬大教堂，一去到見到嗰種震撼感真係講唔出黎<br />\n呢個大教堂係現時世界第八高嘅教堂，地下有個墓室係放左哈布斯家族成員嘅內臟同骨，但未有時間去join tour，頭三日我只係景點門口經過或者行過圈，當做認下路。因為我打算最尾嗰幾日先去睇曬vienna所有野，作一個深度遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下嘅圖都有加少少filter，因為我影相影得唔好睇仲要用iPhone ，唯有用filter搭救，但唔影響原本欣賞嘅效果，<br />\nStephansdom外觀<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/045153_023728784ff1331899b7d999e9ef0bc3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F045153_023728784ff1331899b7d999e9ef0bc3.jpg&h=33e4b1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5j7P6w8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5j7P6w8.jpg&h=f16f347d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nStephansdom入面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/045852_f0d570d5d5c54603c26b76ab4acf47d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F045852_f0d570d5d5c54603c26b76ab4acf47d1.jpg&h=7e6fa311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/045856_ce026c3788fea5f42ad8f27f165f31dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F045856_ce026c3788fea5f42ad8f27f165f31dd.jpg&h=5978d872&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fea3922c098784e38fc8423e18bca859dec59e7","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>salzburg除左去國王湖仲有咩玩</blockquote><br />\nSalzburg 其實頂盡用兩日就行完，我第一日14:00到，都可以係咁兒行囇要行嘅景點，不過嗰度靚仔都幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想留多幾日，呀。。。仲有hallstatt"},{"pid":"9090d29415d945ed58a149d6f3722f4ca6d92842","tid":197293,"uid":51237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:10:10.000Z","msg":"Stephansdom個外牆仲未整好？我1月份去嘅時候已經係咁喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw已正皮，絲打加油繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f613aba245ea3b94dfd755a975e103cdfa2b0e4","tid":197293,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>salzburg除左去國王湖仲有咩玩</blockquote><br />\nSalzburg 其實頂盡用兩日就行完，我第一日14:00到，都可以係咁兒行囇要行嘅景點，不過嗰度靚仔都幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好想留多幾日，呀。。。仲有hallstatt</blockquote><br />\n媾一個"},{"pid":"61572276e78270f18fd3c5e7bb4b73646cde0882","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T21:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Stephansdom個外牆仲未整好？我1月份去嘅時候已經係咁喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw已正皮，絲打加油繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未整好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽人講其實佢長期都維修囉， 依家仲要整埋隔離嗰撻地，好地地都唔知整黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 訓醒先再繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68fbc3fed99f84f90be7917c5e9f7b7ca75d5adc","tid":197293,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"a199e525203a70b0c0f25a8551743b512b1ac467","tid":197293,"uid":3103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推"},{"pid":"91fcc6db5f76b28b3e7ae46cdb471ba821fd06a4","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:29:35.000Z","msg":"之後再去左St. Peter Church 聖彼得教堂，就如好多人所講，外觀真係唔多起眼，教堂門口仲要勁多馬車，如果唔細心d留意真係會發現唔到，整體建築風格為巴洛克式，教堂內部裝修極華麗，真係值得入去睇，我會形容stephansdom係五十幾歲嘅太太，仲成日走去打Botox<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而st peter就係二十幾歲女仔，而呢個女仔內涵比起佢嘅外表更加值得欣賞<br />\n外觀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/161018_f7f65f76e71b6bf3135d359c9b9d45e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F161018_f7f65f76e71b6bf3135d359c9b9d45e0.jpg&h=128da93d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/161518_5ff9ceaa4ca5032d0a90e85039716fe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F161518_5ff9ceaa4ca5032d0a90e85039716fe4.jpg&h=27ff6057&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79aedbeaa5b48a6d30490e8904148fde17e888ef","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"頂部嘅壁畫<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28S1140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28S1140.jpg&h=915c3d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後經過左黑死病紀念柱，見證住黑死病係歐洲嘅歷史<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOnWe48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOnWe48.jpg&h=6f15e1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有茜茜公主博物館岀面，實在太多人，好難影到一張好睇嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163804_78aabf3e678b738cf7a5da9956404644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163804_78aabf3e678b738cf7a5da9956404644.jpg&h=5b8dd1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就咁樣結束左我一日之旅，對於填飽自己個肚，隨便食d野就算<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164439_c6d9d89913fa74ea070ec45aad8dbda9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164439_c6d9d89913fa74ea070ec45aad8dbda9.jpg&h=4d400011&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1049de15033ae2bb561bc719b664905cdf9cbd3","tid":197293,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:59:10.000Z","msg":"munich消費高唔高, 一餐大概幾歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691407dde300259a49b23d78fd0612d1c928049d","tid":197293,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>munich消費高唔高, 一餐大概幾歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申 5月都會Vienna &gt; Hallstatt &gt; Salzburg &gt; Munich<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a22906d624a198d76517d08b25b5843f187898","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T09:01:30.000Z","msg":"頂部嘅壁畫<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28S1140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28S1140.jpg&h=915c3d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後經過左黑死病紀念柱，見證住黑死病係歐洲嘅歷史<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iOnWe48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiOnWe48.jpg&h=6f15e1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有茜茜公主博物館岀面，實在太多人，好難影到一張好睇嘅相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163804_78aabf3e678b738cf7a5da9956404644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163804_78aabf3e678b738cf7a5da9956404644.jpg&h=5b8dd1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就咁樣結束左我一日之旅，對於填飽自己個肚，隨便食d野就算<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164439_c6d9d89913fa74ea070ec45aad8dbda9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164439_c6d9d89913fa74ea070ec45aad8dbda9.jpg&h=4d400011&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac631e489f8bd37dff4f6704bece895542407e68","tid":197293,"uid":77001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T09:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>munich消費高唔高, 一餐大概幾歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對我黎講，一個三文治加杯飲品 6歐內都平，貴嘅就食正餐普遍8-15歐"}]}